<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #eb8e5f;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eb8e5f;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .email-body h1 {
            color: #DF9E7C;
        }
        .email-body p, .email-body h1 {
            text-align: left;
        }
        a:not(.button-link) {
            color: #DF9E7C;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .button-link {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 10px auto;
            background-color: #eb8e5f;
            color: #000000; 
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #eb8e5f;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h2>Fatima's Therapy Services</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <h1>Welcome to Our Clinic</h1>
            <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
            <p>We're excited to have you on board. To get started, please activate your account by clicking the button below:</p>
            <br>
            <a href="{{link}}" target="_blank" class="button-link">Activate Account</a>
            <br>
            <p>This link will expire in one hour. If you did not make this request, please ignore this message.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            Regards,<br>
            The Clinic Team<br>
            <a href="https://www.fatimanaqvi.com">www.fatimanaqvi.com</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
